data.description: This charming home welcomes you with a two-stories foyer and beautiful hardwood floors, a formal dining room that provides the perfect setting for hosting dinner parties and special occasions, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for entertaining guests. The large kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring ample counter space and modern appliances, making meal preparation a joy for any home chef. Enjoy spacious bedrooms that offer comfort and privacy, providing an ideal retreat for every member of the household. The dedicated laundry room ensures that chores are a breeze, providing a practical and organized space for all your laundry needs. Relax and unwind in the fenced backyard, a private retreat that offers a safe space for children to play and for family gatherings under the open sky. Experience the convenience of nearby restaurants and shopping, adding an extra layer of ease to your daily lifestyle. Downtown Augusta is a mere 19 minutes away, providing access to cultural events, entertainment, and a vibrant city life while maintaining the tranquility of suburban living. This property combines comfort, style, and practicality, making it an ideal residence for those seeking a harmonious blend of modern living and convenient amenities.
